  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/cf892175b37161a8022ba79e30759efd.avif?t=1666810851\" width=616 height=186 /></span><br><br>Asha was a great warrior in life, and like all great warriors, she had a great death, having been defeated by her great rival, Kaira the piercing blade. After a long struggle, Kaira's blade pierced her body and Asha fell to the ground, then darkness surrounded her.<br><br>In the darkness the smell of grass fills the environment, Asha gets up out of the earth, lifting the grass in the process, she feels the heat of the sun and soon realizes, she is in Valhalla.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/a9e094c98ebaba3247238731c8ebdd67.avif?t=1666810851\" width=616 height=186 /></span><br>Talk to Valhalla's warriors to learn about them, and hear the stories of their lives being told by Bragi, the god of music and poetry<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/03616669c1bf7d0b6ef1f26fe3d86401.avif?t=1666810851\" width=616 height=186 /></span><br>Defeat all Valhalla warriors to become the champion of the gods. Each warrior has his own combat style, each battle is unique<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/e52b81f532eb44c343a85c5e6294f3db.poster.avif?t=1666810851\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/e52b81f532eb44c343a85c5e6294f3db.webm?t=1666810851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/e52b81f532eb44c343a85c5e6294f3db.mp4?t=1666810851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To defeat the warriors you can count on the help of the Norse gods, such as Thor and Balder<br><br><br><br>Becoming the champion of Valhalla is an achievement only for the truly strong, will you be able to accomplish such an achievement?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/cf892175b37161a8022ba79e30759efd.avif?t=1666810851\" width=616 height=186 /></span><br><br>Asha was a great warrior in life, and like all great warriors, she had a great death, having been defeated by her great rival, Kaira the piercing blade. After a long struggle, Kaira's blade pierced her body and Asha fell to the ground, then darkness surrounded her.<br><br>In the darkness the smell of grass fills the environment, Asha gets up out of the earth, lifting the grass in the process, she feels the heat of the sun and soon realizes, she is in Valhalla.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/a9e094c98ebaba3247238731c8ebdd67.avif?t=1666810851\" width=616 height=186 /></span><br>Talk to Valhalla's warriors to learn about them, and hear the stories of their lives being told by Bragi, the god of music and poetry<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/03616669c1bf7d0b6ef1f26fe3d86401.avif?t=1666810851\" width=616 height=186 /></span><br>Defeat all Valhalla warriors to become the champion of the gods. Each warrior has his own combat style, each battle is unique<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/e52b81f532eb44c343a85c5e6294f3db.poster.avif?t=1666810851\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/e52b81f532eb44c343a85c5e6294f3db.webm?t=1666810851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786130/extras/e52b81f532eb44c343a85c5e